      • processCommand

        public void processCommand(org.bukkit.command.CommandSender sender,
                           java.lang.String[] args)
        Processes all /tpp storage commands. Separates the command into who ran the command and who the command is about, and passes this information to processCommandGeneric
        Parameters:
        sender - The sender of the command
        args - The arguments passed to the command, excluding /tpp storage

      • processCommandGeneric

        public void processCommandGeneric(org.bukkit.entity.Player sender,
                                  org.bukkit.OfflinePlayer commandFor,
                                  java.lang.String[] args)
        The generic processor for /tpp storage [] commands, that takes into account who ran the command and whom the command is about. Analyzes arguments, passes to proper methods, and reports results back to user.
        Parameters:
        sender - The command sender
        commandFor - Who the command is about
        args - The arguments passed to /tpp storage, not including /tpp storage
